{"id":6695,"date":"2018-04-21T12:44:06","date_gmt":"2018-04-21T11:44:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?p=6695"},"modified":"2021-10-25T13:41:07","modified_gmt":"2021-10-25T12:41:07","slug":"arugam-bay-guide","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/arugam-bay-guide\/","title":{"rendered":"Arugam Bay: 7 Best Things To Do"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>About Arugam Bay<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s important to know that the busy season runs from June until August. The waves in this season are world-famous. Parties are going on in the night. Outside of this season, the weather is still great, just no waves, no parties. The season you should go is up to you. Restaurants and shops are open from February until October.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__wrapper video-block__wrapper--breakout\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/VideoObject\">\n                <h3 class=\"video-block__wrapper-title\" itemprop=\"name\">Sri Lanka Road Trip<\/h3>\n\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnail\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23152355\/Thumb-roadtrip-sri-lanka-1-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Sri Lanka Road Trip\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23152355\/Thumb-roadtrip-sri-lanka-1-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2018-07-02 19:46:11\">\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block video-block--mediavine\">\n                    <div class=\"video-block__embed\">\n                        <div class=\"mv-video-target mv-video-id-res9jmcur9x6ybuncu4d\" data-video-id=\"res9jmcur9x6ybuncu4d\" data-volume=\"70\" data-ratio=\"16:9\" data-autoinsert=\"true\" data-disable-jsonld=\"true\"><\/div>\n        