 the whole region.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Find all:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/arugam-bay-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"&#x27B3;&#xA0;Find all:&#xA0;Hotels in Arugam Bay (opens in a new tab)\">Hotels in Arugam Bay<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n<div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155142\/20184632_1824153480932279_5882592022707044352_n.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img class=\"alignnone size-large lazypreload\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155142\/20184632_1824153480932279_5882592022707044352_n-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155142\/20184632_1824153480932279_5882592022707044352_n-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155142\/20184632_1824153480932279_5882592022707044352_n-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155142\/20184632_1824153480932279_5882592022707044352_n-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155142\/20184632_1824153480932279_5882592022707044352_n-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155142\/20184632_1824153480932279_5882592022707044352_n-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/st